modName: Save Game MQ Done Ready For Dragonborn
summary: Save game MQ done, Companions done, Thieves Guild Done, Allot of little quests Done so you can start Dragonborn. No Cheating. Used Start Another Life to begin this game.
descriptionHtml:
I was informed i put the wrong file up. sry, i get confused due to illness. I have re-added Ladygothica, try version 1.1

Done by Request, This is my game I am playing right now. I have made two copies, one female, one male, both have identical gear. 
Big Damm, you wont get the Warpaint unless you download it. TairenSoul Face Tattoo Warpaint by TairenSoul   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25211
No cheats.
No animals were harmed in the making of this file, they just got big boo boo\'s.
I use the Ring of Change Showracemenu fix http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9458
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn_zpse6f06f6b.jpg[/IMG]
The Main Quest is Finished
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn_zpscbcb57a0.jpg[/IMG]
The Companions are Finished  Still a wearwolf.
I sided with the Storm-cloaks.
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/vvbbvbbbbb_zps47aaa234.jpg[/IMG]
I never Married
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/nnnn_zpsd09d7391.jpg[/IMG]
Thieves Guild is finished.
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/bbbbbbbbbb_zpse1d27701.jpg[/IMG]
I have homes in Whiterun, Riften, Markarth, and Solitude, but i have never used Breezehome, it crashes when i enter. 
There is still heaps to do, i did not touch the Dark Brotherhood because i like to kill them all, and others may like to join them. I am not a horder, i sell everything. 
I use SkyUI  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3863/
Skyrim -Community- Uncapper by Ely  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/1175
I have weight of 1507
I have Vilja as a companion follower in the Drunken Huntsmen. You dont need her to play this game.   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26393
Too look like my character you will need 
Children of Skyrim Presets   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21184
Women of Skyrim-Enhanced female normalmaps by zzjay
Apachii Hairs all files
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666
High-Res Female Nord Skin ( yeah i know, she is a imperiel, i changed her race and forgot this, not sure if it will make a difference.)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25531
Better Females By Bella Natural Edition
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812
Better Females by Bella 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26113
Women of Skyrim Face textures
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25588
Women of Skyrim-Enhanced female normalmaps 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20483

Other Mods i was using
Smooth Faces http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/1971
The Eyes of Beauty
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722
Other mods i use, most of the mainstream armor and weapons mods, all unofficial updates, 
ACE - Combat Skills by Athyra - ACE Team   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10037
Duel - Combat Realism by Gabriel Mailhot   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2700
Lots of immersive mods, but that should not make a difference to you. 
If you have any problems let me know and ill do what i can to help.

If you just want to complain, you will be wasting your breath because i won\'t listen. I know there are spelling mistakes in this, but my hands are really sore, today.

When life gives you a keyboard,
make a bunny rabbit.
